   Pause All Audio
  </h1>
  This action can be used to pause all sounds currently playing, but this will not pause any sounds played
  <i>
   after
  </i>
  the action has been called. You can start them playing again using the action
  <a href="Resume_All_Audio.htm">
   Resume All Audio
  </a>
  .
  <h4>
   Action Syntax:
  </h4>
  <br/><img src="https://gms.magecorn.com/Manual/assets/Images/Scripting_Reference/Drag_And_Drop/Reference/Audio/a_Audio_Pause_All_Audio.png"/><br/>
  <h4>
   Example:
  </h4>
  <br/><img src="https://gms.magecorn.com/Manual/assets/Images/Scripting_Reference/Drag_And_Drop/Reference/Audio/e_Audio_Pause_All_Audio.png"/><br/>
  The above action block code will check a global variable and if it evaluates to
  <span>
   true
  </span>
  then all sound is paused, otherwise it is all resumed.
